quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  21,76,"Kandi bibuke intumwa y’Imana Nuhu (iii) mugihe yashikiriza ubutumwa bwiwe aho hambere, natwe twaramwemerera, duca turamurokora hamwe n’abantu biwe mungorane niniya nkizo"
  21,77,"Twaramurokoye kubera abantu bahakanye amajambo yacu, mu vy’ukuri abo bantu bari abantu babi cane, duca tubibiza mumazi bose uko bangana"
  21,78,"Kandi ubibutse kubijanye n’intumwa y’Imana Daudi (iii) hamwe n’intumwa y’Imana Sulaimanu (iii) mugihe baca urubanza kubijanye n’itongo mugihe zarisha muri iryo tongo intungwa z’abandi mw’ijoro, natwe kubera urwo rubanza twari ivyabona"
  21,79,"Duca tubwira intumwa y’Imana Sulaimanu (iii) n’umwe muribo twamuhaye intahe n’ubumenyi, hanyuma duca tugamburutsa imisozi yose hamwe n’intumwa y’Imana Daudi (iii) ihayagiza Imana, tugamburutsa n’inyoni nazone zigamburukira Imana hamwe nawe natwebwe nimubagira ivyo dushaka"
  21,80,"Duca twigisha intumwa y’Imana Daudi (iii) ingene yohingura impuzu z’ingwano kubera mwebwe, kugira ngo zibakingire mungwano zanyu, mbega muzoba muri mubantu bashima"
  21,81,No kuntumwa y’Imana Suleimanu (iii) twara gamburukije umuyaga ukaze cane ugira kumategeko yiwe ngaha kw’Isi twahezagiye natwe nitwebwe dufise ubumenyi bw’ibintu vyose
  21,82,"Twara gamburukije amashetani yibirira mumazi nukugirira ibindi bikorwa bitari ivyo, natwe twari muba bacungera"
  21,83,"N’intumwa y’Imana Ayyubu (iii) mugihe Umuremyi wiwe yamu hamagara avuga ati:- jewe nahuye n’ingorane, nawewe niwe ufise Impuhwe gusumba abandi batanga impuhwe"
  21,84,"Twaramwemereye nukumukurira ingorane yari afise, duca tumuha abantu biwe n’abandi b’akarorero nkabo bari kumwe nabo, n’impuhwe zivuye iwacu hamwe n’icibutso ciza kubantu bagira amasengesho yabo"
  21,85,N’intumwa y’Imana Ismaili (iii) hamwe n’intumwa y’Imana Idrissa (iii) hamwe na Dhul’kifli (iii) abo bose bari muntumwa z’Imana zitenyenya
  21,86,"Duca twinjiza mumpuhwe zacu, kuko bari mubantu beranda"
  21,87,"N’uwitwa Dha-nnuni ariwe ntumwa y’Imana Yunusu (iii) mugihe yagenda nawe bamwihakanye abiwe nawe aca yiyumvira yuko twebwe tutazo mushobora, rero yaciye ahamagara ari mumwijima avuga ati:- ntawundi asengwa bimwe vy’ukuri atari wewe gusa uninahazwa, mu vy’ukuri jewe nari muba hemukiye imitima yabo"
  21,88,"Turamwakirira igisabisho ciwe nukumurokora mugahinda yarimwo, uku rero niko turokora abantu bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  21,89,"N’intumwa y’Imana Zakariya (iii) mugihe yahamagara Umuremyi wiwe avuga at:- Muremyi wanje ntunsige ndi jenyene, na wewe niwe mwiza wabasigirwa ibisigi"
  21,90,"Duca turamwemerera ibisabisho vyiwe nukumuha intumwa y’Imana Yahya (iii), nuguca dukiza umutambukanyi wiwe, ntankeka bari bafise umwete wukugira ineza nukudusaba n’ishaka ryinshi hamwe nugutinya, nabo bari bafise ubugamburutsi ntangere"
  21,91,Nuwikingiye k’umutima wiwe nuguhuhera umutima wacu nukumugira ngo abe hamwe n’umwana wiwe kuba ari ibitangaro ku bantu bose
  21,92,"Mu vy’ukuri aba bantu banyu n’abantu bamwe nanje ndi Umuremyi wanyu, kuri ivyo nimunsenge"
  21,93,"Nabo baca baradohoka kuri rino jambo ryabo riri hagati yabo, kandi nabo bazo garuka iwacu"